{
  "id": "adv_event_2409_01_03",
  "title": "名優、鈴村\n久美子の娘",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――舞台『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』稽古初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――First day of rehearsal for the stage show \"Pretty★Angel\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.1400000333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-enshutu001.m4a",
      "text": "演出を担当する蟻田よ。早速だけど、時間が惜しいわ\n台本の読み合わせを始めます。みんな、いいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Arita‚ in charge of directing. It's early‚ but time's tight\nWe'll begin the script reading. Everyone‚ it's okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.0333334048,
      "endTime": 11.573333652799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.7666669289
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……いよいよだね、瑠依ちゃん。優ちゃんの演技が\nプロの演出家さんの目にどう映るのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Finally here‚ Rui-chan. I wonder how Yu-chan's performance\nwill be perceived by the pro-director…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7666669289,
      "endTime": 19.7614062706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.964648954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。厳しそうな人だし、手がけた舞台の評価も高い\nあの人なら、優に的確な評価を下してくれるはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. He seems strict‚ and the stage he was in charge of was highly rated\nThis person‚ will give Yu an accurate assessment",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.964648954,
      "endTime": 29.1614062706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.2313165108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-enshutu002.m4a",
      "text": "そこっ！　私語は慎みなさい！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! No small talk!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2313165108,
      "endTime": 31.2915205399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3979821602,
      "endTime": 32.7354651371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9387078205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "（まったく……演技が初めての瑠依ちゃんはともかく）\n（すみれちゃんまであんなに浮ついて……困ったもんや）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Seriously… Even Rui‚ who's acting for the first time）\n（Even Sumire is acting so excited… It's troubling）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9387078205,
      "endTime": 42.0168936649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.2053744871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "（さぁ、名優、鈴村久美子の娘――鈴村優）\n（華麗に主役のプカミちゃんを演じさせてもらいますっ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Now‚ let's move on to the daughter of the famous actress‚ Kumiko Suzumura―― Yu Suzumura）\n（The main character‚ Fukami‚ begins its splendid performance!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2053744871,
      "endTime": 51.5030618269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-enshutu003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ鈴村さん、始めてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ Suzumura-san‚ please begin",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7053744871,
      "endTime": 54.385374601500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8387075662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "「エート、キミィーナンダカ、スゴクムズカシイ\nコトバヲツカウミタイダケドォー」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'YOU USINGSOME\nPRETTYDIFFICULTLANGUAGEー'",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8387075662,
      "endTime": 62.4626077889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6720408995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "（ふふ……どうです、うちの演技は。あらあら）\n（蟻田さん、感激し過ぎて目をまん丸にしてるわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Fufu… What do you think of my acting? Oh dear）\n（Arita-san is so moved‚ his eyes are wide open.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6720408995,
      "endTime": 72.50920654129999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.7053742329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-enshutu004.m4a",
      "text": "……鈴村さん。あの……えぇと、少し時間をちょうだい\n…………えぇぇ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Suzumura-san. Ah… hey‚ give me a moment\n…Ehhh~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7053742329,
      "endTime": 80.9987042347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.2053706724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あの蟻田さんが困惑してる！？\n容赦のない演技指導で有名なのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arita-san is confused!?\nHe's famous for his unforgiving acting skills!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2053706724,
      "endTime": 87.1674795706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.370722254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして優の演技は、私みたいな凡人には\n理解出来ない領域に達している、ということなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Could it be that Yuu's acting has reached a level\nthat an average person like me‚ can't comprehend?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.370722254,
      "endTime": 96.0271847326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.2373889207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-enshutu005.m4a",
      "text": "そこっ！　私語は慎むっ！！　……あの、鈴村さん\n一つだけ聞かせて。真面目にやってるのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! No small talk!! …Well‚ Suzumura-san\nLet me ask you just one thing. You're taking this seriously?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2373889207,
      "endTime": 105.7307215928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.4333339692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。今日のために瑠依ちゃん\nすみれちゃんと三人で沢山練習してきましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Rui-chan and Sumire-chan‚ the three of us‚\nhave practiced a lot for today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9373884121,
      "endTime": 113.1204722325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "演出家",
      "speakerNameEn": "Director",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-enshutu006.m4a",
      "text": "そう。そうなのね……なら言わせてもらうわ、鈴村さん\n――あなたド下手。頑張ってこれじゃ、公演は絶対無理",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I got it… Then let me say this‚ Suzumura-san.\n――You're so terrible. If this is all you can do‚ you'll never make the performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3040550787,
      "endTime": 125.57072225399999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5000006359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ？　何言うてますの？　そんな訳ないですやん\nな、なぁ、瑠依ちゃん、すみれちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? What are you talking about? It's no way\nH-Hey‚ Rui-chan‚ Sumire-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.770722254,
      "endTime": 134.716867121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.6373888492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "……なんで二人とも、そんな気まずそうなん？\nえ？　……えぇ？　うちから目を逸らさんとって～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why do you two look so awkward?\nEh? …Ehh? Don't look away from me~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9040555874,
      "endTime": 143.5824001232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.7799576185
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.820722254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "最悪や……\nうちほんまに最低最悪やあぁぁーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Worst…\nI'm really lowest and worstttーー!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.870722254,
      "endTime": 152.7422869284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.9373889207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "大好きな作品だーとか……うちは人気俳優の娘とか……\n全部フリになってもうたやん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my favorite anime… and I'm the daughter of the famous actress…\nBut it's all just a lie!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9373889207,
      "endTime": 161.1951211213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.4040555874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "しかも演出の蟻田さん……\nこないだの「おはテレ」観てたみたいだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And director Arita-san…\nIt seems like he watched 'Oha-Tere'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.4040555874,
      "endTime": 167.289815227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.493057839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……どれだけ厳しいしごきが待ってるのか\n楽しみにしとります",
      "translations": {
