      "text": "……ごめん、優ちゃん。私達も薄々気付いてたんだ\nでも、確信が持てなくて……目を背けちゃってた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry‚ Yu-chan. We all kind of had a feeling it was coming\nBut we weren't sure… and we turned a blind eye…",
        "id": ""
      },
