      "text": "ママ……ありがとう。うちな、アイドルになりたい\n可愛い衣装を着て、歌って、踊るのが、うちの夢",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mom… thank you. I want to be an idol\nSinging‚ dancing‚ wearing cute costumes is my dream",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.9029629467,
      "endTime": 363.64892680630004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 363.83629628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "せやからうち、東京に行きたい。アイドルの最前線で\nうちの力がどこまで通用するか、試してみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want to go to Tokyo. I want to test my skills\non the front lines of idols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.83629628,
      "endTime": 372.7790403444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yumam004.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん……ええよ。私とパパは、ずーっと優の味方や\nたとえ遠く離れても、応援しとる。頑張りや……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes… that's great. Dad and I will always be on your side‚ Yu\nEven if we're far apart‚ we'll support you. Good luck…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.9696296134,
      "endTime": 385.94963564060004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 386.1362890878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、ママ…………大好き",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Mom…… I love you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 386.1362890878,
      "endTime": 389.6181712308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
