      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 400.6696275788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "家族の絆って……力になるよね。私も凄く分かる\nところで優ちゃん、ちょっと純粋な疑問なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Family connections… are so powerful. I totally understand that\nBy the way‚ Yu-chan‚ I have a simple question…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.6696275788,
      "endTime": 412.89250775150003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 407.6333407719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "小さい頃は映画とかドラマによく出てたって言ってた\nよね？　その……その時は大丈夫だったのかなぁって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you appeared in a lot of movies and dramas when you were little‚\nright? Well… I wonder if you were okay then",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 413.0957504349,
      "endTime": 423.2972473221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 423.5004900055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……全部うちが赤ちゃん頃のことやねん\n物心付いてからは……記憶にあるんやと一回だけやな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aha… it was all when I was a baby\nSince I was old enough to understand… I only remember one time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 423.5004900055,
      "endTime": 432.9040952759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 433.1004900055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "二歳とか三歳ぐらいの頃かなぁ……。お母さん主演の\n『針の丘』って映画に、娘役で出たことがあるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Around two or three years old… I appeared in the movie\n\"Needle Hill\" starring my mother‚ as the daughter",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 433.1004900055,
      "endTime": 442.4896280365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 442.7004900055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、それ知ってる！　映画祭で賞を獲ってたよね\nその時の演技はどうだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I know that! It won an award at the film festival\nHow was your acting then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 442.7004900055,
      "endTime": 449.50049000549996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 449.7037326889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "まわりの大人らには「さすがあの鈴村久美子の娘！」\n「天才現る！」なんて褒められとったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The adults around me praised me‚ 'It's a daughter of Kumiko Suzumura!'\n'A genius is here!'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 449.7037326889,
      "endTime": 458.2282228546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 458.4370660223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "今思えば、おだてられとったんやろうなぁ……\nはぁぁ～……このまま消え去りたいわぁ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking back‚ I think they were just flattering me…\nHaah~… I just want to disappear…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 458.4370660223,
      "endTime": 466.7928254523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 467.0037326889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "元気を出して、優。過去はどうあがいても変えられない\nでも、未来はこれからの頑張りで、変えられる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheer up‚ Yu. No matter how you try‚ you can't change your past\nBut you can change your future‚ with your hand",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 467.0037326889,
      "endTime": 475.0118730621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 475.2037326889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "せやな……うちの黒歴史はどうやっても消せんしなぁ\nくよくよすんのは止めや。心機一転、頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right… Our old shame can't be erased no matter what\nStop worrying about it. I'll make a fresh start‚ and do my best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 475.2037326889,
      "endTime": 485.28502560429996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 485.4703993556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_03-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ先生！　うちの演技指導をよろしゅう頼みます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-sensei! Please give me some acting guidance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 485.4703993556,
      "endTime": 490.080535197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
